in neighbouring states over the past year.

77
00:08:36,351 --> 00:08:41,272
At 6.06 this morning
Donnie Pf aster made it three.

78
00:08:41,398 --> 00:08:43,525
6.06?

79
00:08:44,442 --> 00:08:46,486
What's so supernatural about that?

80
00:08:46,611 --> 00:08:51,241
