Maybe you could go over it again.

85
00:09:08,133 --> 00:09:11,386
- I'm a Christian man.
- Then you'll tell me the truth.

86
00:09:11,469 --> 00:09:17,934
Yeah. But I got no idea about
Donnie Pf aster... or how he broke out.

87
00:09:19,436 --> 00:09:23,565
