89
00:09:26,234 --> 00:09:30,488
Yeah, but you had something happen.
You had an incident.

90
00:09:30,572 --> 00:09:32,949
Yeah. Something like that.

91
00:09:33,032 --> 00:09:36,327
You cried out to the guards
that you'd cut your hands.

92
00:09:37,162 --> 00:09:40,832
My fingers, man. I saw them all cut off.

93
00:09:40,915 --> 00:09:43,585
- Others saw them, too.
- I felt them cut off.

94
00:09:43,668 --> 00:09:48,840
- How do you explain that?
- God works in mysterious ways, brother.

95
00:09:51,843 --> 00:09:55,180
Glory. Amen.

