121
00:12:40,345 --> 00:12:43,973
- You're looking at my hands.
- You need a buff and polish.

122
00:12:45,850 --> 00:12:47,810
What are you? A freak?

123
00:12:49,646 --> 00:12:51,689
I... I just got out of prison.

124
00:12:51,773 --> 00:12:55,526
Hey, Missy. Leave the customers alone!

125
00:12:57,028 --> 00:12:58,529
I'll do it for free.

126
00:12:58,613 --> 00:13:02,033
You just got out of prison,
and you want to give me a manicure?

127
00:13:03,076 --> 00:13:05,411
I'll even do your cuticles.

128
00:13:05,536 --> 00:13:09,499
