132
00:13:21,219 --> 00:13:26,724
The grace of God got you out, and it's
the only thing that will keep you out.

133
00:13:27,433 --> 00:13:30,812
- I thought you were kidding.
- He's chosen you, Donnie.

134
00:13:38,653 --> 00:13:40,780
Later.

135
00:13:43,491 --> 00:13:45,702
- You called them on me.
- No.

136
00:13:46,577 --> 00:13:48,913
- Then do something.
- I have a car.

137
00:13:54,752 --> 00:13:58,756
- We aren't going to make it to the car.
- It's within his power.

138
00:14:04,095 --> 00:14:05,680
Glory. Amen.

139
00:14:07,473 --> 00:14:09,225
Glory. Amen.

140
