141
00:15:17,168 --> 00:15:21,714
- Was he here?
- Well, um... we're trying to determine that.

142
00:15:21,798 --> 00:15:25,635
- Did you see him?
- Well, that's a good question.

143
00:15:25,718 --> 00:15:29,305
We thought we saw something,
but apparently we didn't.

144
00:15:29,555 --> 00:15:33,184
We got a call about a possible
sighting of the suspect.

145
00:15:34,227 --> 00:15:37,855
- Well, something happened here, huh?
- A guy got hit by a car.

146
00:15:41,067 --> 00:15:45,071
Prison chaplain, it turns out.
A Reverend Orison.

147
00:15:45,196 --> 00:15:48,699
Paramedics took him to the hospital.
He's in bad shape.

148
00:15:48,783 --> 00:15:52,328
("Don't Look Any Further" by John Hiatt
over stereo)

149
00:15:54,330 --> 00:15:57,291
Excuse me, uh, could
you turn that up, please?

150
00:15:57,375 --> 00:15:59,252
Yeah.

151
00:16:19,147 --> 00:16:22,567
You're lucky to be alive, Reverend Orison.

152
00:16:22,775 --> 00:16:25,903
- Who are you?
- Special Agent Dana Scully.

153
